	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />275ns or faster is sufficient for the CPU bus (i.e. PRG ROM, SRAM).
<br />175ns or faster is needed for the PPU bus (CHR ROM, CHR RAM).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


